Viggle,is,a,social,TV,platform,that,rewards,users,for,checking,in,to,shows,they,are,watching,Users,earn,loyalty,rewards,for,watching,TV,shows,The,Viggle,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Viggle,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,likes,and,reminders,managing,account,information,and,retrieving,show,information